osternal air space.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.070183,0.1334,0.13107,0.11641,0.099047,0.091415,0.081023,0.071641,0.073025,0.052217,0.044232,0.036335],"unified_progress":[0.061115,0.10236,0.10977,0.11494,0.11243,0.1002,0.091554,0.081385,0.085315,0.058119,0.046171,0.036641]},{"section":7,"text":"First, the smoking history is a big red flag.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.067032,0.11434,0.12882,0.12246,0.10493,0.085244,0.077518,0.068952,0.060881,0.069914,0.050284,0.049617],"unified_progress":[0.072412,0.087239,0.094626,0.10387,0.099853,0.090806,0.091687,0.08608,0.07863,0.081762,0.062948,0.050086]},{"section":8,"text":"He's been smoking a lot (1.5 packs a day) for years, which is a major risk factor for chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD).","dimension":11,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.06359,0.10613,0.10439,0.10161,0.098769,0.099554,0.088086,0.083401,0.073748,0.070789,0.059036,0.050885],"unified_progress":[0.091702,0.1152,0.10257,0.093887,0.089922,0.089802,0.082563,0.085009,0.073269,0.068082,0.058977,0.049015]},{"section":9,"text":"The symptoms of progressive dyspnea and dry cough are classic for COPD.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.052164,0.096838,0.10086,0.098819,0.096042,0.09337,0.090033,0.087765,0.078133,0.07774,0.067974,0.060266],"unified_progress":[0.073554,0.088627,0.090546,0.093294,0.092458,0.093706,0.089417,0.089172,0.081887,0.082394,0.06938,0.055567]},{"section":10,"text":"The physical exam findings like barrel chest and hyperresonance on percussion point towards hyperinflation of the lungs, which is typical in COPD due to air trapping.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.045646,0.090667,0.097999,0.10005,0.098037,0.096813,0.093982,0.087934,0.085944,0.076521,0.067077,0.059329],"unified_progress":[0.05596,0.080485,0.092632,0.10025,0.10074,0.099379,0.094938,0.090313,0.087916,0.077487,0.065683,0.054216]},{"section":11,"text":"Prolonged expiration and wheezing could be from the obstruction in the airways.","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.045909,0.089632,0.094089,0.09636,0.096707,0.097764,0.095843,0.09071,0.08756,0.077907,0.068602,0.058917],"unified_progress":[0.055548,0.078615,0.088611,0.094732,0.098645,0.099519,0.095946,0.092687,0.090096,0.080324,0.06933,0.055948]},{"section":12,"text":"Now, the presence of clubbing is interesting.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043232,0.084986,0.099761,0.10199,0.097826,0.091049,0.089317,0.085159,0.081806,0.085325,0.073268,0.066286],"unified_progress":[0.046895,0.073668,0.084507,0.094318,0.097085,0.095475,0.096332,0.093313,0.090109,0.090846,0.076997,0.060454]},{"section":13,"text":"Clubbing isn't typical in COPD alone.","dimension":6,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035675,0.074138,0.089257,0.097183,0.099975,0.097797,0.098641,0.094059,0.088352,0.08628,0.07561,0.063032],"unified_progress":[0.06666,0.068394,0.081274,0.088936,0.094938,0.097139,0.096845,0.095733,0.090228,0.088718,0.074096,0.05704]},{"section":14,"text":"Wait, but maybe there's another condition here.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033694,0.074204,0.093629,0.099983,0.10031,0.096417,0.094696,0.091952,0.088419,0.087718,0.075204,0.063778],"unified_progress":[0.044021,0.07947,0.089132,0.099674,0.099109,0.096306,0.097856,0.094065,0.088891,0.088825,0.071059,0.051594]},{"section":15,"text":"The pitting edema in the legs and puffy face (maybe ascites or hepatic issues?) could suggest cor pulmonale, which is right-sided heart failure secondary to lung disease.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033417,0.072355,0.084345,0.092392,0.097347,0.10052,0.10117,0.096567,0.093163,0.085874,0.077217,0.065638],"unified_progress":[0.03813,0.065295,0.080434,0.089974,0.096294,0.10107,0.098854,0.097762,0.096706,0.09047,0.080317,0.064698]},{"section":16,"text":"COPD can lead to pulmonary hypertension and then cor pulmonale.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027958,0.062016,0.075913,0.087549,0.096631,0.10157,0.10444,0.10051,0.095555,0.091775,0.082889,0.073193],"unified_progress":[0.036019,0.055627,0.069711,0.078632,0.08848,0.099051,0.099163,0.1012,0.10158,0.099915,0.093201,0.077412]},{"section":17,"text":"The edema and facial puffiness might be due to fluid retention from heart failure.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.0241,0.056123,0.069978,0.082132,0.093074,0.10045,0.10587,0.1038,0.10135,0.095211,0.0902,0.077705],"unified_progress":[0.029257,0.046449,0.059663,0.070014,0.083401,0.096556,0.098758,0.10361,0.10901,0.11033,0.10639,0.086559]},{"section":18,"text":"The X-ray findings: hyperinflation, flattened diaphragm, and increased retrosternal space (which I think is part of the hyperinflation, making the AP diameter larger).","dimension":5,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034134,0.077261,0.088715,0.095352,0.095101,0.098817,0.097419,0.091825,0.1003,0.08241,0.073893,0.064773],"unified_progress":[0.036214,0.069289,0.08729,0.099465,0.10535,0.10446,0.10255,0.093816,0.094922,0.083588,0.067652,0.055406]},{"section":19,"text":"All these are consistent with COPD, especially emphysema.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.034002,0.073297,0.088152,0.094917,0.096031,0.09446,0.094683,0.090149,0.088464,0.08763,0.077484,0.08073],"unified_progress":[0.036597,0.0639,0.079211,0.090336,0.094011,0.098509,0.096809,0.09413,0.092843,0.089734,0.084103,0.079817]},{"section":20,"text":"But wait, the clubbing...","dimension":12,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028144,0.063214,0.080788,0.089456,0.09494,0.096308,0.09821,0.097082,0.097034,0.093357,0.087344,0.074124],"unified_progress":[0.050708,0.066738,0.079096,0.089511,0.093763,0.094475,0.096322,0.096092,0.094192,0.095077,0.081587,0.062438]},{"section":21,"text":"Hmm.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.31065,0.05181,0.052654,0.061397,0.062325,0.065277,0.062504,0.07101,0.072218,0.06728,0.070008,0.052861],"unified_progress":[0.21762,0.083739,0.064767,0.064787,0.073817,0.073806,0.087773,0.080447,0.077059,0.06218,0.057268,0.056741]},{"section":22,"text":"Clubbing can be seen in some lung conditions like lung cancer, interstitial lung disease, or chronic infections.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030917,0.06904,0.060433,0.1035,0.11216,0.10643,0.10875,0.10057,0.091179,0.084137,0.074535,0.058364],"unified_progress":[0.050342,0.074748,0.06351,0.095649,0.10223,0.10172,0.10265,0.10034,0.095056,0.088474,0.073156,0.052129]},{"section":23,"text":"But in COPD, clubbing isn't common.","dimension":6,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025994,0.059959,0.076471,0.088787,0.097002,0.10038,0.10446,0.10215,0.097861,0.093483,0.084729,0.068717],"unified_progress":[0.073938,0.068191,0.076879,0.084163,0.091019,0.093231,0.094075,0.096713,0.091921,0.091984,0.077679,0.060206]},{"section":24,"text":"Maybe the patient has another issue?","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.31165,0.05124,0.052618,0.061578,0.063369,0.065236,0.06315,0.071115,0.07114,0.066755,0.069408,0.052742],"unified_progress":[0.22997,0.088918,0.062037,0.064788,0.073588,0.072468,0.090336,0.078817,0.075482,0.060218,0.054071,0.049311]},{"section":25,"text":"Let me think again.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.30847,0.052862,0.26125,0.058268,0.040758,0.038992,0.035698,0.041576,0.044504,0.04402,0.042661,0.030941],"unified_progress":[0.19082,0.062546,0.25202,0.081501,0.05621,0.054249,0.053197,0.060611,0.0587,0.048078,0.042814,0.03926]},{"section":26,"text":"The alcohol use\u2014could there be liver disease contributing to the edema and facial changes?","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039